<style>

}

    display: -ms-flexbox;
    display: flex;
    -webkit-box-align: center;
    -ms-flex-align: center;
    align-items: center;
    -webkit-box-pack: center;
    -ms-flex-pack: center;

}

    clear: both;
}

    width: 100%;

}

    color: #fff;

}

    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 5px;
